      <guid>http://yoshiharuyamashita.com/post/introducing-blackburn-hugo-theme/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello world!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ve recently been experimenting with &lt;a href=&#34;//gohugo.io/&#34;&gt;Hugo&lt;/a&gt;, which is a static site generator created by &lt;a href=&#34;//github.com/spf13&#34;&gt;spf13&lt;/a&gt;. My experience is still rudimentary but so far it&amp;rsquo;s been fun using it. Hugo makes it really easy to setup, configure and customise a website.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A BIG thank you to spf13 for creating such a cool project!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As part of learning Hugo, I&amp;rsquo;ve had a go at creating a theme for it. It&amp;rsquo;s called Blackburn and is available from &lt;a href=&#34;//github.com/yoshiharuyamashita/blackburn&#34;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This serves as my first post.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
